"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"BBC Verify has looked at many videos of fibre-optic drone attacks by the Lebanese armed group.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drone Attacks by Lebanese Group\",            \"translated_version\": \"BBC Verify ha visto muchos videos de ataques con drones de fibra \u00f3ptica por el grupo armado liban\u00e9s.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques con Drones por Grupo Liban\u00e9s\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president, after his meeting in Beijing, warned against the island declaring independence.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President Warns Island\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU., despu\u00e9s de su reuni\u00f3n en Beijing, advirti\u00f3 a la isla sobre declarar independencia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. Advierte a Isla\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Wildlife experts had criticized the operation, saying it would only make the animal more upset.\",            \"english_title\": \"Experts Criticize Animal Operation\",            \"translated_version\": \"Expertos en vida silvestre criticaron la operaci\u00f3n, diciendo que solo har\u00eda al animal m\u00e1s molesto.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Expertos Critican Operaci\u00f3n Animal\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Charges might come next week in a case about Cuba's shooting down of two planes in 1996.\",            \"english_title\": \"Charges in Cuba Plane Case\",            \"translated_version\": \"Cargos podr\u00edan venir la pr\u00f3xima semana en un caso sobre el derribo de dos aviones por Cuba en 1996.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cargos en Caso de Aviones en Cuba\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Eight people were hurt, four seriously, before people nearby chased and stopped the man.\",            \"english_title\": \"Eight Hurt in Incident\", 